		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">躁动沙虫发射7个星砂弹，下落的区域围成一个扇形，每个星砂弹造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">躁动沙虫发射抹尘追弹，追踪玩家位置，依次在玩家处下落，一共下落6枚，每枚抹尘追弹造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">躁动沙虫发射一个风蚀弹，该风蚀弹沿直线行进，触碰风蚀弹或待其爆炸均造成<span color="#7fffd7">250%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
